description: The Czech Republic is quite a difficult country. And public health care is no exception. Mother of this poor student had fallen ill and needed a treatment. Unfortunately, waiting list was very long. Her son was determined to help. He even tried to bribe a doctor. That corrupt bastard asked for 35 000 Crowns. Now my client was looking for money everywhere. Without any success. When he was starting to despair, he found my advertisement and called me. I was moved by his story and I wanted to help but I am a business man. I don´t give up my money for free. The boy wasn´t happy but agreed to do what I asked for. And he was absolutely amazing at it! Honestly, I was surprised he had a girlfriend because he deep-throated my cock like if it was his hobby.
title: Debt Dandy 219
